
README for akonadi


POST-INSTALL
MySQL is the default database backend; please install the mysql package for it
to work.
You can also use SQLite as a more lightweight backend.
In order to do so, please edit
/home/YOURUSERNAME/.config/akonadi/akonadiserverrc as follows:

[Debug]
Tracer=null

[%General]
Driver=QSQLITE3

[QSQLITE3]
Name=/home/YOURUSERNAME/.local/share/akonadi/akonadi.db
StartServer=true
